fields.name: Andrea Bocchio Jewelry
fields.description: Brookly-based Peruvian designer Andrea Bocchio makes a bold, fresh look with her jewelry collection. Expect bright colors, lush textures and unexpected details on trend with traditional knitting and crocheting methods, perfect for adding a pop of color and making a statement.

fields.name: Kahri
fields.description: Hip, funky, rocker chic, sophisticated yet sexy women's contemporary clothing and accessories.

fields.name: Katie Bartels gemstone jewelry
fields.description: handmade gemstone bracelets, necklaces, and earrings

fields.name: Amy DiGregorio
fields.description: AMY DiGREGORIO is a collection of women's accessories inspired from the designer's globetrotting. Jewelry and headpieces are created from a luscious mix of Indian leather, Miyuki glass, Tibetan Naga shell, silk, faceted gemstones, precious metals, and other carefully found objects.

fields.name: FOUR LA
fields.description: FOUR LA is a contemporary lifestyle boutique providing the latest clothing and accessory trends to men and women who value style in the four roles they may play: casual self, trendsetter, savvy professional or upscale socialite. From Day to Night, Work to Play find designer and independent local brands like Mark & James by Badgley Mischka, Plastic Island, Fifteen-Twenty, Alternative Apparel, Ouroboros Designs and many more!

fields.name: Toasty Toes
fields.description: stunable support is toasty toes woohoo

fields.name: LLG Designs
fields.description:
LLG Designs are unique Jewelry, Clothing and Accessories individually designed and handmade.

Most of my pieces are limited editions and one of a kind. Custom orders are always welcomed.

fields.name: Lucca Couture
fields.description: Fresh and new fashion at its finest, Lucca Couture bridges the gap between high-end fashion and everyday street style. Lucca Couture’s unique and versatile collections exude a high fashion aesthetic, yet its ready-to-wear prices define it as a universal brand for anyone who enjoys originality and style.

fields.name: One OAK by Sara
fields.description: One OAK by Sara is handcrafted jewelry.  Not synthetic or mass produced, One OAK by Sara incorporates authentic materials from around the world.  In many cases, gemstone pendants are left in their natural form and metals are mixed for a chic, but earthy look.  Enjoy creating your own personalized look centered around the one-of-a-kind nature of gemstones & vintage components.

fields.name: MUSAS
fields.description: After graduating from graphic design school in Brazil and doing some soul searching, Adriana realized that she wanted to embrace her femininity and create beautiful jewelry for women like herself. The Adriana’s jewelry line is the stunning culmination of pouring herself – her Brazilian heritage, love for life, and feminine independence - into her work.

fields.name: FRIENDS with BENEFITS
fields.description: We are a women's high fashion lifestyle brand.  We bring a combined 20 years of experience.  Separately, we have different points of view but together we create a modern, collection that whispers sensuality.  Our focus is on cut, fit and luxury.  Our clothes are designed for the independent fashion spirit.

fields.name: Kimberly Jarman Apparel
fields.description: I'm a 29 year old wife and mother of one with a passion for designing and fashion.  My line Rondure is a sophisticated mix of classic and fun with a hit of retro.  It's very figure flattering because it's all about the curves!

fields.name: Beija-Flor Jeans
fields.description: Beija-Flor Jeans is a premium jeans line designed in Greenville, SC. Our jeans are known for their flattering fit, and super soft Brazilian denim. We have been featured several times as "figure fixing" jeans! Your search for the perfect jeans is over!
